        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>“How do I pay for a temporary ABC permit and what is the fee?”

Retrieved Results:

Knowledge Article → confidence: 0.45 (general permit info)

Web Search → confidence: 0.76 (fee page + payment links)

✅ Agent Response:

The fee for a temporary ABC permit is $50.
You can make payments directly through the NCABC payment portal.

💵 Permit Fee Details along with the URL From where It got the information

💳 Make a Payment Online along with the URL From where It got the information</description>
